item.description:

[quote="``jason, post:4, topic:195761"][quote author=billygotshot link=topic=260291.msg2159105#msg2159105 date=1207301478]

There’s only one error, and I’m guessing you’re using an outdated script? Or you don’t have SRL.

I have srl and i guess they are outdated? could i just simply downgrade scar so it works with srl? or do you know where i can get the newest srl
[/quote]
SRL is not compatible with SCAR, downgrading scar will not change anything as the extra procedures are in SRL.
What i mean is that you are calling on SRL which is external.
Downgrading SRL may work though.[/quote]
What are you talking about? SRL is compatible with SCAR and always will be. To download the latest SRL Repository version, please refer to this thread to install SRL.
